comments: Take him! You won\'t regret him!! He\'s very informed and is easy to pass

Professor Murray is awesome! His lectures hones your attention to a fine tuned focus. He has a love for history and political science and most students engage in his class, because that thirst a knowlege is there. A rare breed and a great teacher! Thanks for one hell of a class Prof Murray, you are the best! Sign up, you will not reget it!

yes, you do have to memorize terms but they\'re all the terms in the text. he basically lectures and he\'s entertaining. all you really have to do is memorize terms and do a group presentation which isn\'t really that hard. It\'s super easy if you just show up and pay attention to what is supposed to be due and such.
In this class, you must memorize a long, long list of political terms and their definitions. I found this class to be useless.
Really Nice Guy, Very Funny. Not Your Usual PoliSci Class...Better. The Class Is Exciting and Keeps Your Attention. He\'s A Bit Unorganized But Other Than That, Everyone Should Take This Class!
